    <item>
      <title>从已经存在的octopress新建环境</title>
      <link>https://xixitalk.github.io/blog/2013/06/19/clone-from-exist-octopress/</link>
      <pubDate>Wed, 19 Jun 2013 18:45:41 +0800</pubDate>
      
      <guid>https://xixitalk.github.io/blog/2013/06/19/clone-from-exist-octopress/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;场景需求：为已经存在的octopress博客在另一个目录或者主机新建一个octopress发布环境&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;h3 id=&#34;获得source和master分支代码&#34;&gt;获得source和master分支代码&lt;/h3&gt;

&lt;pre&gt;&lt;code&gt;$ git clone -b source git@github.com:xixitalk/xixitalk.github.com.git octopress
$ cd octopress
$ git clone git@github.com:xixitalk/xixitalk.github.com.git _deploy 
&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description>
